ProductName: Liquid I.V.® Hydration Multiplier® Zero Sugar Green Grape Electrolyte Drink Mix Packets
ProductSubCategory: Liquid I.V.® Hydration Multiplier® Zero Sugar Green Grape Electrolyte Drink Mix Packets
Description:
Liquid I.V.® Hydration Multiplier® is a great-tasting, non-GMO electrolyte drink mix powered by Cellular Transport Technology (CTT)®️ to hydrate faster and more efficiently than water alone. Typically when you drink fluids, they pass through the entire digestive system, losing water before your body can absorb it. CTT® uses a precise ratio of sodium, glucose and potassium to create an osmotic force that allows water to be delivered to the bloodstream earlier as it goes through the digestive system. One stick contains three times the electrolytes of traditional sports drinks, along with five essential vitamins.
Non-GMO
Vegan
Gluten- dairy and soy-free
No artificial ingredients
Convenient, travel-friendly, single-serving packets
Contains five essential vitamins: B3, B5, B6, B12 and C
Our Mission: Defeating Dehydration Globally - We donate millions of servings of Liquid I.V.® to developing nations around the world; Liquid I.V.® has donated over 10 million servings to people in need around the world.

ProductName: Liquid I.V.® Hydration Multiplier® Sugar Free Rainbow Sherbert Electrolyte Drink Mix Packets
ProductSubCategory: Liquid I.V.® Hydration Multiplier® Sugar Free Rainbow Sherbert Electrolyte Drink Mix Packets
Description:
Liquid I.V.® Hydration Multiplier® is a great-tasting, non-GMO electrolyte drink mix powered by Cellular Transport Technology (CTT)®️ to hydrate faster and more efficiently than water alone. Typically when you drink fluids, they pass through the entire digestive system, losing water before your body can absorb it. CTT® uses a precise ratio of sodium, glucose and potassium to create an osmotic force that allows water to be delivered to the bloodstream earlier as it goes through the digestive system. One stick contains three times the electrolytes of traditional sports drinks, along with five essential vitamins.
Non-GMO
Vegan
Gluten- dairy and soy-free
No artificial ingredients
Convenient, travel-friendly, single-serving packets
Contains five essential vitamins: B3, B5, B6, B12 and C
Our Mission: Defeating Dehydration Globally - We donate millions of servings of Liquid I.V.® to developing nations around the world; Liquid I.V.® has donated over 10 million servings to people in need around the world

It’s the Sweeeeeeeet One! Satisfy your craving for flavor with the authentic taste of Diet Dr Pepper! It’s not your ordinary soda and it’s definitely not a cola. Description:
Liquid I.V.® Hydration Multiplier® is a great-tasting, non-GMO electrolyte drink mix powered by Cellular Transport Technology (CTT)®️ to hydrate faster and more efficiently than water alone. Typically when you drink fluids, they pass through the entire digestive system, losing water before your body can absorb it. CTT® uses a precise ratio of sodium, glucose and potassium to create an osmotic force that allows water to be delivered to the bloodstream earlier as it goes through the digestive system. One stick contains three times the electrolytes of traditional sports drinks, along with five essential vitamins.
Non-GMO
Vegan
Gluten- dairy and soy-free
No artificial ingredients
Convenient, travel-friendly, single-serving packets
Contains five essential vitamins: B3, B5, B6, B12 and C
Our Mission: Defeating Dehydration Globally - We donate millions of servings of Liquid I.V.® to developing nations around the world; Liquid I.V.® has donated over 10 million servings to people in need around the world

ProductSubCategory: Liquid I.V.® Hydration Multiplier® Strawberry Lemonade Electrolyte Drink Mix Packets
Description:
Liquid I.V.® Hydration Multiplier® is a great-tasting, non-GMO electrolyte drink mix powered by Cellular Transport Technology (CTT)®️ to hydrate faster and more efficiently than water alone. Typically when you drink fluids, they pass through the entire digestive system, losing water before your body can absorb it. CTT® uses a precise ratio of sodium, glucose and potassium to create an osmotic force that allows water to be delivered to the bloodstream earlier as it goes through the digestive system. One stick contains three times the electrolytes of traditional sports drinks, along with five essential vitamins.
Non-GMO
Vegan
Gluten- dairy and soy-free
No artificial ingredients
Convenient, travel-friendly, single-serving packets
Contains five essential vitamins: B3, B5, B6, B12 and C
Our Mission: Defeating Dehydration Globally - We donate millions of servings of Liquid I.V.® to developing nations around the world; Liquid I.V.® has donated over 10 million servings to people in need around the world

ProductName: ReaLime® 100% Lime Juice
ProductSubCategory: ReaLime® 100% Lime Juice
Description:
When you’re looking for a splash of lemon or lime juice, nothing beats ReaLemon and ReaLime. Made with 100% lemon and lime juice from concentrate, you get the benefit of the great taste of real juice without the hassle of cutting into fresh lemons or limes. First introduced in Chicago in 1934 by Irving Swartzburg, ReaLemon and ReaLime have been trusted brands that deliver only the highest quality of lemon and lime juice. ReaLemon and ReaLime are space-saving kitchen sidekicks, ideal for adding a delicious twist of lemon or lime to your favorite seafood and poultry recipes. Although they’re both great for use in a variety of marinades, they have their unique uses as well. Use ReaLemon to brighten up both hot and cold beverages or use ReaLime to add a bright splash of flavor to salads and dressings. When you want the real taste of real lemon or lime, simply reach for ReaLemon and ReaLime.
REAL FLAVOR: Made with 100% lemon and lime juice from concentrate
FRESH TASTE: Get the taste of real juice without the hassle of cutting into fresh lemons or limes
NATURALLY GOOD: ReaLemon and ReaLime are caffeine-free, gluten-free and sodium-free
FOOD ENHANCER: ReaLemon and ReaLime are space-saving kitchen sidekicks, adding a delicious twist of lemon or lime to your favorite seafood, poultry and marinades

Description:
TAZO® Regenerative Awake® English Breakfast is made from ingredients grown with regenerative agriculture practices and principles that improve the health of the soil and ensure better care for the farmers who grow our teas. Need something with enough kick to perk up those early mornings and afternoon slumps? This bold, full-bodied blend of organic Assam and Kenyan black teas is packed with enough caffeine to have you parting ways with your usual cup of joe. Brewing's easy: just bring 8 fl oz fresh, filtered water to a boil, pour over your tea bag, steep for 5 minutes—and voilà! You’ve got a bold cup of smooth, no-nonsense black tea. Comes packaged with 16 individual tea bags for your sipping pleasure, and it's Kosher, Fair Trade and Non-GMO Project Verified. At TAZO®, we’re not just a tea company. We’re a group of tea-obsessed people on a mission to challenge the status quo. This doesn’t stop at exciting, new tea blends; it continues with making the world a better place. That means investing in regenerative growing practices. Stepping up for environmental justice. ProductName: Liquid I.V.® Hydration Multiplier® Tropical Punch Electrolyte Drink Mix Packets
ProductSubCategory: Liquid I.V.® Hydration Multiplier® Tropical Punch Electrolyte Drink Mix Packets
Description:
Liquid I.V.® Hydration Multiplier® is a great-tasting, non-GMO electrolyte drink mix powered by Cellular Transport Technology (CTT)®️ to hydrate faster and more efficiently than water alone. Typically when you drink fluids, they pass through the entire digestive system, losing water before your body can absorb it. CTT® uses a precise ratio of sodium, glucose and potassium to create an osmotic force that allows water to be delivered to the bloodstream earlier as it goes through the digestive system. One stick contains three times the electrolytes of traditional sports drinks, along with five essential vitamins.
Non-GMO
Vegan
Gluten- dairy and soy-free
No artificial ingredients
Convenient, travel-friendly, single-serving packets
Contains five essential vitamins: B3, B5, B6, B12 and C
Our Mission: Defeating Dehydration Globally - We donate millions of servings of Liquid I.V.® to developing nations around the world; Liquid I.V.® has donated over 10 million servings to people in need around the world

ProductName: Snapple® Fruit Punch Juice Drink
ProductSubCategory: Snapple® Fruit Punch Juice Drink
Description:
Snapple Fruit Punch is an explosion of fruit flavor, perfectly mixing orange, pineapple, grape, and apple. Now that's a delicious taste worth fighting for. Do yourself a flavor! Snapple Fruit Punch is all natural, gluten-free, made from 10% real juice, and contains no artificial flavors or sweeteners. Even better, our 16oz and 20oz bottles are recyclable and made from 100% recycled plastic, excluding the cap and label. Snapple always brings the flavor. That's what we have been doing ever since we were a small brand created by three friends in the New York area. We started out by selling our apple juice to health clubs in 1973. Since then, we have expanded our flavor portfolio throughout the 80s into teas, fruit drinks, and lemonades. Snapple went national in the early 90s, and now you can find us in more than 30 flavors and in all 50 states across the country. And for an extra dose of fun, don't forget to check out our Snapple 'Real Facts' under our caps!

When you’re looking for a splash of lemon or lime juice, nothing beats ReaLemon and ReaLime. Use ReaLemon to brighten up both hot and cold beverages or use ReaLime to add a bright splash of flavor to salads and dressings. When you want the real taste of real lemon or lime, simply reach for ReaLemon and ReaLime.

TAZO® Regenerative Chai is made from ingredients grown with regenerative agriculture practices and principles that improve the health of the soil and ensure better care for the farmers who grow our teas. This robust blend of USDA organic black teas combines rich spices like cinnamon, ginger, and cardamom to bring you the full-bodied cup of chai of your dreams. Plus, it’s got the perfect amount of caffeine: not too much, not too little—just enough to give you a boost, sans the jitters. Our Organic Chai comes packaged with 16 individual tea bags for your sipping pleasure, and it's Kosher, Fair Trade and Non-GMO Project Verified. By the way, brewing's also a cinch: Just bring fresh, filtered water to a boil, carefully pour water over your black tea bag, and let it steep for 5 minutes (the longest 5 minutes, we know). Then, you’re good to take that first sip! At TAZO®, we’re a group of tea-obsessed people on a mission to challenge the status quo. This doesn’t stop at exciting, new tea blends; it continues with making the world a better place. That means investing in regenerative growing practices. Stepping up for environmental justice. And shining a spotlight on important issues (like the climate crisis) to help our communities—and the planet. So choose your favorite blend, brew a cup, and let's stir things up.
TAZO® Regenerative – Organic Chai brings together the richest spices from all around the world
This blend combines bold black teas with warm notes of ginger, cardamom, and cinnamon
Caffeine? Just the right for an invigorating morning or afternoon pick-me-up black tea
Easy prep: bring fresh, filtered water to a boil, pour over tea bag, and steep for 5 minutes

Liquid I.V.® Hydration Multiplier® is a great-tasting, non-GMO electrolyte drink mix powered by Cellular Transport Technology (CTT)®️ to hydrate faster and more efficiently than water alone. Typically when you drink fluids, they pass through the entire digestive system, losing water before your body can absorb it. One stick contains three times the electrolytes of traditional sports drinks, along with five essential vitamins.

ProductName: Dr Pepper® Soda Bottle
ProductSubCategory: Dr Pepper® Soda Bottle
Description:
Satisfy your craving for flavor with the unique taste of Dr Pepper! It’s not your ordinary soda and it’s definitely not a cola. It’s the sweet treat that can’t be beat. So, whether you enjoy the original or any of the varieties like Dr Pepper® Cherry and our latest innovation, Dr Pepper & Cream Soda, you’ll get the satisfying flavor that only Dr Pepper can deliver straight to your taste buds. It’s a refreshing favorite that’s always smooth and delicious at dinner, lunch or breakfast (we won’t judge you!). Although you can enjoy the unique flavor all on its own, you can also pair it with food. Dr Pepper is the perfect companion for everything from a full meal like pizza, burgers or rotisserie chicken to a quick snack like pastries, chocolates or your favorite candy. You can’t go wrong with a Dr Pepper when you want to satisfy your sweet cravings. Give your tastebuds something to cheer for with.
ALL DAY REFRESHMENT: There’s no wrong time of the day to enjoy a Dr Pepper. Crack a Pepper at dinner, lunch or breakfast (we won’t judge you)
ALWAYS A TREAT: Rich, smooth and delicious every time, Dr Pepper packs a mouthful of flavor with every sip (you’re welcome, taste buds)
PERFECT PAIRING: Pizza, burgers or rotisserie chicken, Dr Pepper is the perfect companion for your next meal
UNIQUE TASTE: Dr Pepper is the uniquely satisfying beverage whether you enjoy the original or any of the varieties like Dr Pepper Cherry and our latest innovation, Dr Pepper & Cream Soda
